data.description: This eye-catching beauty is a solid brick ranch on a corner lot in Channahon that has a total of 5 bedrooms and 5 full baths!! So many extras in this house: Main floor has 4 full baths, Master bedroom includes 2 of those, plus additional sitting room area! Finished basement can be used for related living or added living space, with 2 more bedrooms and a full bath, a family room, and kitchen area! Additional 36 x 9 space in basement can be rec room, play room; whatever works for you! Doors to extra large Trex deck exit from family room and bedroom. 2 car garage is heated. Furnace, AC and water heater new within last 2 years. Come see it for yourself! It's not every day you find a ranch like this!!
